---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About" 
  description="About Willem van der Maden - AI Design Researcher at IT University of Copenhagen"
>
  <!-- Bio Section -->
  <section class="container-content py-12 md:py-16">
    <h1 class="mb-2" data-scroll-reveal>About</h1>
    <p class="text-ink-muted text-lg mb-10"></p>
    
    <div class="prose max-w-none space-y-6 text-lg">
      <p data-scroll-reveal>
        I'm Dr. Willem van der Maden, a researcher at the IT University of Copenhagen. In a nutshell, I work on the design of AI systems for <span class="marker-highlight">human flourishing</span>.
      </p>

      <p data-scroll-reveal>
        By <em>design</em>, I mean I approach AI from a sociotechnical perspective: not just model development, but the whole system where technology meets society. By <em>human flourishing</em>, I mean steering AI so it genuinely helps people thrive, whether that's through better workflows, improved wellbeing, or more meaningful experiences.
      </p>

      <p data-scroll-reveal>
        In practice, this means I study how people actually build and evaluate AI products. My current research focuses on how practitioners <span class="marker-highlight">evaluate LLM-based systems</span> in production, where the real decisions happen and where we can anticipate problems before they scale.
      </p>

      <p data-scroll-reveal>
        I teach <em>AI for Designers</em> at the bachelor level and <em>Datafication and Representation</em> at the master level at ITU Copenhagen. My work draws on HCI, design research, and mixed methods to bridge the gap between what AI can do and what people actually need it to do.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Work History Section -->
  <section class="container-content py-12 md:py-16 border-t border-border" data-scroll-reveal>
    <div class="md:flex md:gap-16">
      <h2 class="text-ink-muted text-lg font-heading mb-8 md:mb-0 md:w-24 flex-shrink-0">Work</h2>
      
      <div class="flex-1">
        <p class="mb-6 text-ink-muted" data-scroll-reveal>
          Key positions throughout my career:
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <!-- ITU Copenhagen -->
          <a 
             href="https://www.itu.dk/" 
             target="_blank" 
             rel="noopener noreferrer"
             class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between p-4 rounded-md hover:bg-cream-dark hover:shadow-soft hover:-translate-y-[1px] transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out no-underline group"
             data-work-card
          >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <img 
                src="/itu.webp" 
                alt="IT University of Copenhagen" 
                class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full object-cover"
                width="40"
                height="40"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading font-medium text-ink group-hover:text-cobalt transition-colors text-base">
                  Postdoctoral Researcher
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted">IT University of Copenhagen</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <span class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-2 sm:mt-0 pl-14 sm:pl-0">Jan 2024 – Present</span>
          </a>
          
          <!-- TU Delft -->
          <a 
             href="https://www.tudelft.nl/" 
             target="_blank" 
             rel="noopener noreferrer"
             class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between p-4 rounded-md hover:bg-cream-dark hover:shadow-soft hover:-translate-y-[1px] transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out no-underline group"
             data-work-card
          >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <img 
                src="/flame.png" 
                alt="TU Delft" 
                class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full object-cover bg-white"
                width="40"
                height="40"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading font-medium text-ink group-hover:text-cobalt transition-colors text-base">
                  Ph.D. Candidate
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted">TU Delft</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <span class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-2 sm:mt-0 pl-14 sm:pl-0">Dec 2019 – Dec 2023</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Connect Section -->
  <section class="container-content py-12 md:py-16 border-t border-border" data-scroll-reveal>
    <div class="md:flex md:gap-16">
      <h2 class="text-ink-muted text-lg font-heading mb-8 md:mb-0 md:w-24 flex-shrink-0">Connect</h2>
      
      <div class="flex-1">
        <p class="mb-6 text-ink-muted" data-scroll-reveal>
          Feel free to connect with me through any of these platforms:
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
          <a 
             href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/wlavandermaden/" 
             target="_blank" 
             rel="noopener noreferrer"
             class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-md border border-border hover:border-cobalt hover:shadow-soft hover:-translate-y-[1px] hover:text-cobalt transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out no-underline group"
             data-scroll-reveal
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-ink-muted group-hover:text-cobalt transition-colors flex-shrink-0">
              <path d="M19 3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2zm-.5 15.5v-5.3a3.26 3.26 0 0 0-3.26-3.26c-.85 0-1.84.52-2.32 1.3v-1.11h-2.79v8.37h2.79v-4.93c0-.77.62-1.4 1.39-1.4a1.4 1.4 0 0 1 1.4 1.4v4.93zM6.88 8.56a1.68 1.68 0 0 0 1.68-1.68c0-.93-.75-1.69-1.68-1.69a1.69 1.69 0 0 0-1.69 1.69c0 .93.76 1.68 1.69 1.68m1.39 9.94v-8.37H5.5v8.37z"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="flex-1 font-heading text-ink group-hover:text-cobalt transition-colors">LinkedIn</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-ink-muted group-hover:text-cobalt transition-colors rotate-45 flex-shrink-0">
              <path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          
          <a 
             href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=_9ZGOcAAAAAJ&hl=da" 
             target="_blank" 
             rel="noopener noreferrer"
             class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-md border border-border hover:border-cobalt hover:shadow-soft hover:-translate-y-[1px] hover:text-cobalt transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out no-underline group"
             data-scroll-reveal
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-ink-muted group-hover:text-cobalt transition-colors flex-shrink-0">
              <path d="M12 3L1 9l11 6l9-4.91V17h2V9M5 13.18v4L12 21l7-3.82v-4L12 17z"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="flex-1 font-heading text-ink group-hover:text-cobalt transition-colors">Google Scholar</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-ink-muted group-hover:text-cobalt transition-colors rotate-45 flex-shrink-0">
              <path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          
          <a 
            href="mailto:willem.maden@gmail.com"
            class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-md border border-border hover:border-cobalt hover:shadow-soft hover:-translate-y-[1px] hover:text-cobalt transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out no-underline group"
            data-scroll-reveal
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-ink-muted group-hover:text-cobalt transition-colors flex-shrink-0">
              <path d="m20 8l-8 5l-8-5V6l8 5l8-5m0-2H4c-1.11 0-2 .89-2 2v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V6a2 2 0 0 0-2-2"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="flex-1 font-heading text-ink group-hover:text-cobalt transition-colors">Email</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-ink-muted group-hover:text-cobalt transition-colors rotate-45 flex-shrink-0">
              <path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
